the laser frequency.

00:10:58.580 --> 00:11:02.330
If you drive an atom, if you
drive a harmonic oscillator

00:11:02.330 --> 00:11:05.390
with a laser frequency,
the harmonic oscillator

00:11:05.390 --> 00:11:09.720
