00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:11.940
We discussed that a while ago.

00:11:11.940 --> 00:11:14.640
So therefore, the
dipole moment oscillates

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:17.690
at the laser frequency.

00:11:17.690 --> 00:11:23.510
And their two components, u
and v-- since our laser field

00:11:23.510 --> 00:11:30.330
