00:11:33.595 --> 00:11:37.750
vector the in phase part
of the dipole moment,

00:11:37.750 --> 00:11:42.470
and the in quadrature
phase of dipole moment.

00:11:42.470 --> 00:11:45.840
If you didn't pay attention
what I said the last five

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:48.430
minutes, that's OK, you
can just start here,

00:11:48.430 --> 00:11:52.230
saying the expectation value
of the dipole moment oscillates

00:11:52.230 --> 00:11:54.010
with a laser frequency.

00:11:54.010 --> 00:11:56.930
And as for any harmonic
oscillator, or harmonic

00:11:56.930 --> 00:11:59.770
oscillator type system,
there is one component

00:11:59.770 --> 00:12:01.432
which is in phase,
and one component

00:12:01.432 --> 00:12:02.390
which is in quadrature.

00:12:06.710 --> 00:12:08.760
Fast forward.

00:12:08.760 --> 00:12:09.910
OK.

00:12:09.910 --> 00:12:13.020
And you know from any
