00:24:27.070 --> 00:24:29.030
And that's usually very fast.

00:24:29.030 --> 00:24:30.840
So you can make
the assumption when

00:24:30.840 --> 00:24:34.650
an atom moves to a changing
electric field, at every point

00:24:34.650 --> 00:24:37.910
in the electric field,
