00:51:36.890 --> 00:51:38.360
Well, we'll get there.

00:51:38.360 --> 00:51:43.060
And it will again
be-- the energy--

00:51:43.060 --> 00:51:46.720
will be extracted through
spontaneous emission

00:51:46.720 --> 00:51:48.860
from all those side
[INAUDIBLE] and all that.

00:51:48.860 --> 00:51:50.845
So we have to trace
down the energy,

00:51:50.845 --> 00:51:52.220
and we successfully
will do that.

00:51:52.220 --> 00:51:55.180
But energy can be subtle.

00:51:55.180 --> 00:51:55.930
Forces are simple.

