00:58:15.590 --> 00:58:19.330
Actually, everything is
a Raman process here.

00:58:19.330 --> 00:58:22.160
Because in laser
cooling, in everything

00:58:22.160 --> 00:58:26.125
which involves the mechanical--
the motion, the external degree

00:58:26.125 --> 00:58:30.560
freedom of the atoms-- we have
an atom in one momentum state.

00:58:30.560 --> 00:58:33.760
We go-- light scattering always
has to involve the excited

00:58:33.760 --> 00:58:39.940
state-- and then we go down
to a different momentum state.

00:58:39.940 --> 00:58:42.760
So therefore, laser
cooling is nothing else

00:58:42.760 --> 00:58:47.329
than Raman processes in the
external degree of freedom

00:58:47.329 --> 00:58:48.960
of the atom.

00:58:48.960 --> 00:58:51.780
You may be used to
[INAUDIBLE] Raman process

00:58:51.780 --> 00:58:54.105
more when you start in
one hyperfine state,

00:58:54.105 --> 00:58:57.140
or for molecules in one
vibration rotation state,

00:58:57.140 --> 00:59:00.950
and you go to another
one, but, well,

00:59:00.950 --> 00:59:03.180
for vibration, and
rotational states,

00:59:03.180 --> 00:59:06.640
and hyperfine states of it,
Raman is used all the time.

00:59:06.640 --> 00:59:09.970
I usually used it also
for the external motion,

00:59:09.970 --> 00:59:13.630
because I think it
clearly brings out

00:59:13.630 --> 00:59:15.790
common features between
all those different Raman

00:59:15.790 --> 00:59:17.850
processes.

00:59:17.850 --> 00:59:25.280
So you can actually say that the
reactive force is a stimulated

00:59:25.280 --> 00:59:27.990
Raman process between two
momentum states, where

00:59:27.990 --> 00:59:31.350
both legs are stimulated
by laser beams.

00:59:31.350 --> 00:59:34.100
In a standing wave, it
would be-- the two legs--

00:59:34.100 --> 00:59:36.990
would be stimulated by the
two travelling wave components

00:59:36.990 --> 00:59:38.950
of the standing wave.

00:59:38.950 --> 00:59:44.300
Whereas the dissipative force
is spontaneous Raman process,

00:59:44.300 --> 00:59:47.327
where one leg is driven by
the laser, and the other one

00:59:47.327 --> 00:59:48.660
comes with spontaneous emission.

