01:24:56.460 --> 01:24:58.490
find other cooling
schemes, where

01:24:58.490 --> 01:25:02.440
we will calculate-- with
the appropriate model--

01:25:02.440 --> 01:25:04.390
the heating and the cooling.

01:25:04.390 --> 01:25:06.340
And I don't have to
repeat this part.

01:25:06.340 --> 01:25:08.510
The moment I calculate
the heating, the momentum

01:25:08.510 --> 01:25:10.980
diffusion, and I
calculate the friction,

01:25:10.980 --> 01:25:14.540
I know what the limiting
temperatures is.

01:25:14.540 --> 01:25:20.775
Again, when I said, the
energy is kt over 2, you know,

01:25:20.775 --> 01:25:24.640
of course, kinetic energy is
kt over 2 times the number

01:25:24.640 --> 01:25:25.820
of degrees of freedom.

01:25:25.820 --> 01:25:27.740
I assumed 1D, here.

01:25:27.740 --> 01:25:29.755
So in everything I've
